snippet.title: Click and Slay Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Click & Slay is an Adventure Idle Clicker in its Pre Alpha Stage. Upgrade your Arsenal while you explore unknown lands and slay the creatures within.

Game Link: https://clickandslaystudios.itch.io/click-slay
Discord:https://discord.gg/PBpUMn8yre
Twitter:https://twitter.com/ClickSlayStudio



Music: www.bensound.com
